frames.caption: A cheerful rabbit wearing a red and white knitted hat is playfully perched on a snowman, holding a wooden cup in one paw. The snowman is adorned with a striped scarf and has a friendly smile, set against a backdrop of snow-covered houses and trees.
frames.description: The scene depicts a whimsical winter setting in a quaint village. A rabbit and a snowman are the central figures, surrounded by charming, snow-laden cottages and evergreen trees, creating a festive and joyful atmosphere.

frames.caption: A cheerful rabbit wearing a red and white knitted hat embraces a snowman adorned with a striped scarf and a top hat. The scene is set in a snowy village with cozy, snow-covered houses in the background. The rabbit's playful expression and the snowman's smile create a joyful and whimsical atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene takes place in a quaint, snowy village during winter. A rabbit is playfully interacting with a snowman, adding to the festive and cheerful ambiance. The background features charming houses with snow-laden roofs, suggesting a peaceful, holiday setting.
